Node.RefEnglish: {woman daughter of daughter of daughter of}

Node.Notes: To give your emission occurs only 4 times in OT. The other 3 times--Lv18:23; 20:15; and Num5:20--do not have of semen, which is interpreted as specification here.
Assumes elision: the native and the alien ... shall not do ... Alternatively, this np in apposition to implied you (pl) subject of previous clause.
